name: Danni Lowinski
overview: Danni Lowinski is a hairdresser in need of money who decides to become a lawyer.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Same table, new shopping center! This season Danni gets in trouble with tax inspection; Niels opens his new store, and the shopping centre gets a new security guard. Piotr surprises Danni by getting a job and a house! Danni couldn't be more happy, but will it last?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: In the first episode of the new season, Niels opens his new shop. Danni helps a truck driver who was involved in a hit-and-run with a child. Meanwhile, Danni gets a visit from a tax inspector.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: There's a new security guard in the shopping center, but not everyone is pleased by it. Danni helps Anne, who cannot read nor write. But how do you solve such a case when your client doesn't want everyone to know about it?

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Danni has her hands full with gambling in a hospital, and a paranoid cop. Jeroen has a secret, and Jos and Elly are introduced.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Piotr finally has a job. Danni helps a beggar who lives in a villa and some prostitutes whose workplaces are in jeopardy.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Danni wonders if Jos really is happy. A little girl steals Danni's purse, but she seems to have a bright future. Danni tries to find out how a man could literally work himself to death.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Danni couldn't be more happy: Piotr got a home of his own. Jeroen meddles in Danni's cases more and more, and an insurance case gets out of hand.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A blind pianist wants a divorce and bachelorette party escalates when a cop is taken for a stripper. But Danni and Lieke think of something extraordinary to make it all okay.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: A surrogate mother needs Danni's help when the parents do not want the baby any longer. Lieke catches her lover with another woman and takes some sweet revenge. Elly really wants to involve Danni in her wedding, which bugs her a lot.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: A charge against a pharmacuetical company needs to go away as soon as possible. Merkelbach, silent partner of Smits & van Loon, wants Danni to take the case. A chance to play with the big boys. Will Danni finally be able to get rid of her folding table and have a real office?

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Elly wants Danni and Lieke to be her bridemaids, complete with kitschy dresses. Meanwhile, Danni and her friends try to help a family circus from bankruptcy. However, the 'grand finale' of the show that night, ends in a small disaster.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: A boy gets accused of stalking and asks Danni for help. When Piotr takes a woman home who wants to move in with them right away, Danni revolts and gives her dad an ultimatum.
